c: 6
v: 50
t: "Say: \"I do not say to you, at me (are) God`s safes/storages (treasures), and I do not know the unseen/absent ,and I do not say to you that I am (an) angel/king/owner , that I follow except what (is) transmitted/revealed to me.\" Say: \"Do the blind, and the seeing become equal/alike, so do you not think"